The paper focuses on natural language understanding and specifically on the task of extractive question answering. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv category of Computer Science - Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel model architecture that uses recurrent networks, which are commonly used in the sub-fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) as it involves finding relevant information from a given text. Finally, the paper's focus on improving performance suggests that it may also belong to the sub-field of neural networks (cs.NE).
